Test Plan

Objectives
	The website automationpractice.com is an online retail store. This test plan will ensure that the website is functioning properly. 

Scope
	The objective is to test as many critical areas as possible. This will include
		- registering for an account
		- signing in to an account
		- the functionality of search criteria 
		- the functionality of online payment options

Assumptions
	The tests will prove that the site is ready on the user end.
	
Risks
	

Test Approach
	We will use a combination of automated and manual tests using Java Code in Eclipse.

Test Environment
	The tests will be conducted in Eclipse, using Java code.

Test Schedule
	The more critical tests will be conducted first. These would be 
		-payment options
		-account registration

Deliverables
	-Test Plan
	-Test Results
	